\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5.1}{\ignorespaces Hallucination comparison on an out-of-domain query. \textit {Left:} Baseline LLM without the agentic layer generates an unsolicited, ungrounded response connecting weather to climate change in Pakistan. \textit {Right:} Full pipeline with Router Agent active correctly classifies the query as out-of-domain and declines to generate.}}{61}{figure.5.1}%
\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5.2}{\ignorespaces RAG Evaluation Report generated by the Deepeval framework. Scores shown are for the English evaluation suite (10 cases). Answer Relevancy and Faithfulness both achieved 1.000; Contextual Precision scored 0.609; Contextual Recall scored 0.750; Hallucination scored 0.175 (lower is better). Overall pass rate: 6/8 eligible cases.}}{65}{figure.5.2}%
